DESCRIPTION: AMG GLE 53 Coupe. The soul of a sports car, the skills of an SUV, and the elegance of a coupe unite to accelerate the pulse rate of Mercedes-AMG passion. Electrified torque whisks you ahead amid a range of driving wizardry.

AMG E 53 4MATIC+ COUPE. There's no feeling quite like opening up an AMG coupe. The E 53 wraps the industry-advancing innovation of the E-Class with a powertain that brings classic muscle into the future.

AMG G 63 SUV. Two renowned legacies of handcraftsmanship unite in the G 63: The globe-tested endurance of the G-Class, and the track-proven performance of AMG. The G 63 reasserts that timelessness can be delivered with a true sense of urgency.

When you're born from the racing legacy of the AMG C-Class, driving wide-open is a way of life. The biturbo, four-seat C 43 Cabriolet features a power top that can turn a breeze into an invigorating rush.
The 382 handcrafted horsepower AMG CLA 45 is the most powerful car in its class, and arguably the most seductive as well.

The BMW M3 vehicles combine powerful proportions and distinctive four-door 3-box design with the sportiness typical of M. Leading these bold characters is the BMW M3 Competition Sedan with its impressive 510 hp and 479 ft/lb of torque. Equipped with a high-performance BMW M TwinPower Turbo power unit, 8-speed M Steptronic with Drivelogic, optional all-wheel drive M xDrive, Active M Differential and numerous technologies derived from motorsport, it guarantees maximum driving dynamics – both in everyday use and on the race track.
In the new BMW M4 CSL everything is designed with a view to enabling the experience of uncompromising motorsport DNA in everyday use.
The athletic BMW 5 Series Sedan delivers 523 hp and impresses with an especially balanced combination of sportiness, comfort and efficiency.

THE NEW BMW M8 Competition Cabriolet. Experience sporty driving pleasure at the highest level – with the impressively powerful the new BMW 8 Series Cabriolet M Automobiles: The new BMW M8 Competition Cabriolet combines pure M genes with supreme exclusivity – for driving adventures full of sporting flair and luxury. The new BMW M850i xDrive Cabriolet impresses with a unique synthesis of comfort, performance and efficiency.

The BMW X6 M Automobiles demonstrate their extroverted dominance with outstanding driving dynamics, expressive M design and unrivalled agility. The BMW X6 M Competition with M xDrive inspires with a luxurious interior and driving dynamics defined by motor racing genes.
Model S Plaid has the quickest acceleration of any vehicle in production. Updated battery architecture for all Model S trims enables back-to-back track runs without performance degradation.

Model 3 comes with the option of dual motor all-wheel drive, 20” Überturbine Wheels and Performance Brakes for total control in all weather conditions. A carbon fiber spoiler improves stability at high speeds, all allowing Model 3 to accelerate from 0-100 km/h* in as little as 3.3 seconds.

With the most power and quickest acceleration of any SUV, Model X Plaid is the highest performing SUV ever built. All Model X powertrains, with updated battery architecture, can deliver instant torque at any speed.

Tesla All-Wheel Drive has two ultra-responsive, independent electric motors that digitally control torque to the front and rear wheels—for far better handling, traction and stability control. Model Y is capable in rain, snow, mud and off-road.

Cybertruck is built with an exterior shell made for ultimate durability and passenger protection. Starting with a nearly impenetrable exoskeleton, every component is designed for superior strength and endurance, from Ultra-Hard 30X Cold-Rolled stainless-steel structural skin to Tesla armor glass.
